<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Collectividual</title>
  <meta name="description" data-i18n-meta="meta_description" content="Collectividual is a psycho-social and cultural project for reflection, experimentation, shared language, and symbolic tools." />
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#EBEBE3;
      --surface:rgba(255,255,255,0.50);
      --text:#27655D;
      --sage:#96B1AA;
      --muted:#7D9C97;
      --accent:#E97F33;
      --border:rgba(39,101,93,0.12);
      --shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(39,101,93,0.05);
      --radius:28px;
      --max:1200px;
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman",serif;
      background:var(--bg);
      color:var(--text);
      line-height:1.55;
      -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
      text-rendering:optimizeLegibility;
    }

    .sans{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif}
    .container{max-width:var(--max);margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}
    .page{display:none}
    .page.active{display:block}
    .section{padding:88px 0}
    .muted-section{background:rgba(150,177,170,.18)}

    header{
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      z-index:50;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      background:rgba(235,235,227,0.92);
      backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    }
    .header-inner{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      min-height:78px;
      gap:24px;
    }
    .header-right{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:18px;
    }
    .logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;text-decoration:none}
    .wordmark{display:flex;align-items:center;font-size:1.95rem;line-height:1;letter-spacing:-0.03em}
    .wordmark .orange{color:var(--accent)}
    .wordmark .green{color:var(--text)}
    .mark{
      display:inline-block;
      width:.78em;
      height:.78em;
      margin:0 .04em;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid rgba(233,127,51,.22);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(235,235,227,0.95) 0 8%, transparent 9%),
        repeating-conic-gradient(from 0deg, #E97F33 0deg 8deg, rgba(233,127,51,0.18) 8deg 10deg);
    }
    nav{display:flex;gap:22px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:flex-end}
    nav a{
      text-decoration:none;
      color:var(--text);
      opacity:.82;
      font-size:14px;
      font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    }
    nav a:hover{opacity:1}

    .lang-toggle{
      display:inline-flex;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:999px;
      padding:4px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.35);
      gap:4px;
    }
    .lang-btn{
      border:0;
      background:transparent;
      color:var(--text);
      min-width:44px;
      min-height:34px;
      border-radius:999px;
      cursor:pointer;
      font:600 12px/1 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      letter-spacing:.08em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      opacity:.75;
    }
    .lang-btn.active{
      background:var(--text);
      color:var(--bg);
      opacity:1;
    }

    .mobile-nav-toggle{
      display:none;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.35);
      color:var(--text);
      min-height:38px;
      padding:0 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      cursor:pointer;
      font:600 12px/1 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      letter-spacing:.08em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .success-wrap{max-width:var(--max);margin:18px auto 0;padding:0 24px}
    .success-message{
      display:none;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      background:rgba(150,177,170,.18);
      padding:16px 18px;
      border-radius:24px;
      font:14px/1.7 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      color:rgba(39,101,93,.86);
      box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(39,101,93,.04);
    }

    .eyebrow,.small-label,.tool-label{
      display:inline-block;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      padding:8px 12px;
      border-radius:999px;
      font:12px/1.2 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.18em;
      opacity:.72;
    }
    .tool-label{border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.12);color:rgba(235,235,227,.78)}

    .hero{position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    .orb{position:absolute;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid rgba(39,101,93,.18)}
    .orb.one{width:260px;height:260px;left:-90px;top:40px;background:rgba(150,177,170,.20)}
    .orb.two{width:180px;height:180px;right:56px;top:92px;border-color:rgba(125,156,151,.5);background:radial-gradient(circle at 35% 35%, rgba(235,235,227,.96) 0%, rgba(150,177,170,0.52) 36%, rgba(125,156,151,0.34) 68%, rgba(39,101,93,0.08) 100%)}
    .orb.three{width:220px;height:220px;left:34%;bottom:-60px;border-color:rgba(233,127,51,.35);background:rgba(233,127,51,.10)}

    .hero-grid{
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1.25fr) minmax(320px,.75fr);
      gap:46px;
      padding:88px 0 104px;
      align-items:end;
    }
    h1{font-size:68px;line-height:1.03;margin:18px 0 0;max-width:860px;letter-spacing:-0.03em}
    h2{font-size:46px;line-height:1.08;margin:0;letter-spacing:-0.025em}
    h3{font-size:30px;line-height:1.18;margin:0 0 12px}
    h4{font-size:22px;line-height:1.25;margin:0 0 12px}
    .hero-copy,.body-copy,.section-copy,.lab-copy,.join-copy,.tool-copy,.resource-copy,.card-copy{
      font:16px/1.9 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      opacity:.84;
    }
    .hero-copy{font-size:19px;max-width:760px;margin-top:20px}
    .manifesto-fragment{font-size:32px;line-height:1.42;margin:18px 0}

    .cta-row,.link-row{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .cta-row{margin-top:34px}
    .btn,.action-btn,.back-btn{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      gap:8px;
      min-height:46px;
      padding:0 18px;
      border-radius:18px;
      text-decoration:none;
      font:500 14px/1.2 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      cursor:pointer;
      transition:transform .14s ease, opacity .14s ease, background .14s ease;
    }
    .btn:hover,.action-btn:hover,.back-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px)}
    .btn-primary,.action-btn.primary{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border:0}
    .btn-secondary,.action-btn.secondary,.back-btn{background:transparent;color:var(--text);border:1px solid rgba(39,101,93,.22)}

    .card,.lab-card,.library-card,.tool-card,.box,.resource-card{
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      background:var(--surface);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
    }
    .card,.box{padding:28px}
    .lab-card,.library-card,.tool-card,.resource-card{padding:24px}
    .resource-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,.36)}
    .card{align-self:end}
    .divider{height:1px;background:rgba(39,101,93,.1);margin:20px 0}
    .icon-dot{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid rgba(39,101,93,.14);background:radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(233,127,51,0.35) 0%, rgba(125,156,151,0.28) 55%, rgba(235,235,227,0.85) 100%);margin-bottom:14px}

    .section-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:40px;align-items:start}
    .section-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:end;gap:24px;margin-bottom:40px}
    .section-top p{max-width:560px}
    .grid-2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:24px}
    .grid-3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));gap:24px}
    .grid-4{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));gap:18px}

    .library-thumb{height:144px;border-radius:22px;background:rgba(125,156,151,.25);margin-bottom:22px}
    .tool-section{background:var(--text);color:var(--bg)}
    .tool-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.10)}
    .tool-copy{color:rgba(235,235,227,.82)}
    .featured-card{background:rgba(233,127,51,.08);border-color:rgba(233,127,51,.18)}

    .join-wrap{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1fr) minmax(320px,.9fr);
      gap:32px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.45);
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:32px;
      padding:38px 40px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }
    form{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;justify-content:center}
    input{
      width:100%;
      min-height:50px;
      padding:12px 16px;
      border-radius:18px;
      border:1px solid rgba(39,101,93,.14);
      background:var(--bg);
      color:var(--text);
      font:15px/1.4 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    }
    .form-note{margin-top:12px;font:12px/1.8 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rgba(39,101,93,.63)}

    .resource-title{font-size:24px;margin-bottom:10px}
    .manifesto-list{margin:0;padding-left:18px}
    .manifesto-list li{margin:0 0 10px}
    .page-title{font-size:62px;line-height:1.03;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin:18px 0 0}

    footer{padding:32px 0 46px}

    .freuds-room-shell{
      margin-top:18px;
      padding:18px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:24px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.46);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }
    .freuds-room-intro{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1fr) auto;
      gap:18px;
      align-items:end;
      margin-bottom:16px;
    }
    .freuds-room-intro-copy{
      margin:8px 0 0;
      color:var(--muted);
      font:14px/1.8 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      max-width:780px;
    }
    .freuds-room-frame{
      width:100%;
      min-height:1480px;
      border:0;
      display:block;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.55);
    }
    .freuds-room-mini-note{
      color:var(--muted);
      font:12px/1.7 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      margin:0;
    }

    .clv-auth-shell{
      margin:40px auto 0;
      padding:28px;
      border:1px solid rgba(39,101,93,.12);
      border-radius:28px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.62);
      color:#244c47;
    }
    .clv-auth-shell *{box-sizing:border-box}
    .clv-auth-kicker{
      display:inline-block;
      padding:6px 12px;
      border:1px solid rgba(39,101,93,.14);
      border-radius:999px;
      font:600 11px/1.2 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      letter-spacing:.12em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:#5a7772;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.55);
    }
    .clv-auth-title{
      margin:14px 0 8px;
      font:400 clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.6rem)/1.05 Georgia,"Times New Roman",serif;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
      color:#244c47;
    }
    .clv-auth-copy{
      margin:0 0 18px;
      max-width:760px;
      color:#5a7772;
      font:15px/1.8 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    }
    .clv-auth-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;
      gap:18px;
      align-items:start;
      margin-top:18px;
    }
    .clv-auth-panel{
      border:1px solid rgba(39,101,93,.12);
      border-radius:22px;
      padding:18px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.72);
    }
    .clv-auth-panel h3{
      margin:0 0 12px;
      font:400 1.2rem/1.15 Georgia,"Times New Roman",serif;
      letter-spacing:-.02em;
      color:#244c47;
    }
    .clv-auth-benefits{
      margin:0;
      padding-left:18px;
      color:#5a7772;
      font:14px/1.8 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    }
    .clv-auth-tabs{
      display:flex;
      gap:8px;
      margin-bottom:14px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }
    .clv-auth-tab,
    .clv-auth-btn{
      appearance:none;
      border:1px solid rgba(39,101,93,.14);
      border-radius:15px;
      background:transparent;
      color:#244c47;
      min-height:42px;
      padding:0 14px;
      cursor:pointer;
      font:600 13px/1.2 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      transition:.15s ease;
    }
    .clv-auth-tab.is-active,
    .clv-auth-btn-primary{
      background:#d97834;
      border-color:#d97834;
      color:#fff;
    }
    .clv-auth-btn-subtle{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.6);
    }
    .clv-auth-row{
      display:grid;
      gap:8px;
      margin-bottom:12px;
    }
    .clv-auth-label{
      color:#5a7772;
      font:600 12px/1.3 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      letter-spacing:.08em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }
    .clv-auth-input{
      width:100%;
      min-height:46px;
      padding:0 14px;
      border:1px solid rgba(39,101,93,.14);
      border-radius:15px;
      background:#fffdf8;
      color:#244c47;
      font:15px/1.4 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    }
    .clv-auth-note,
    .clv-auth-status{
      color:#5a7772;
      font:13px/1.7 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    }
    .clv-auth-status{
      min-height:24px;
      margin:8px 0 0;
    }
    .clv-auth-actions{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:10px;
      margin-top:12px;
    }
    .clv-auth-hidden{display:none !important}
    .clv-auth-userbox{
      border:1px solid rgba(39,101,93,.12);
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:14px;
      background:rgba(241,236,226,.55);
      margin-bottom:12px;
    }
    .clv-auth-userbox strong{
      display:block;
      margin-bottom:4px;
      font:600 15px/1.4 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    }
    .clv-auth-userbox span{
      color:#5a7772;
      font:13px/1.7 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    }
    @media (max-width: 860px){
      .clv-auth-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .clv-auth-shell{padding:18px}
    }
  

    .footer-copy{font:13px/1.8 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;opacity:.66}

    @media (max-width: 1060px){
      nav{display:none}
      .mobile-nav-toggle{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
      .hero-grid,.section-grid,.join-wrap,.grid-2,.grid-3,.grid-4,.section-top{grid-template-columns:1fr;display:grid}
      .section-top{align-items:start}
      .header-inner{align-items:flex-start;padding:14px 0}
      .header-right{width:100%;justify-content:space-between}
      h1{font-size:50px}
      h2{font-size:38px}
      h3{font-size:26px}
      .page-title{font-size:46px}
      .manifesto-fragment{font-size:28px}
      .section{padding:72px 0}
      .hero-grid{padding:74px 0 86px}
      .wordmark{font-size:1.72rem}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a href="#" class="logo" onclick="showPage('home'); return false;">
        <div class="wordmark"><span class="orange">c</span><span class="mark"></span><span class="orange">llecti</span><span class="green">vidual</span></div>
      </a>
      <div class="header-right">
        <nav>
          <a href="#manifesto" onclick="goToSection('manifesto'); return false;" data-i18n="nav_manifesto">Manifesto</a>
          <a href="#laboratories" onclick="goToSection('laboratories'); return false;" data-i18n="nav_laboratories">Laboratories</a>
          <a href="#library" onclick="goToSection('library'); return false;" data-i18n="nav_library">Library</a>
          <a href="#tools" onclick="goToSection('tools'); return false;" data-i18n="nav_tools">Tools</a>
          <a href="#join" onclick="goToSection('join'); return false;" data-i18n="nav_join">Join</a>
        </nav>
        <button type="button" class="mobile-nav-toggle" onclick="toggleMobileNav()" data-i18n="mobile_menu">Menu</button>
        <div class="lang-toggle" aria-label="Language toggle">
          <button type="button" class="lang-btn active" data-lang-btn="en" onclick="setLanguage('en')">EN</button>
          <button type="button" class="lang-btn" data-lang-btn="tr" onclick="setLanguage('tr')">TR</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div id="mobile-nav" class="container" style="display:none;padding:12px 24px 0;">
    <div class="card" style="padding:16px 18px;">
      <div class="link-row" style="gap:10px;">
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#manifesto" onclick="goToSection('manifesto'); toggleMobileNav(false); return false;" data-i18n="nav_manifesto">Manifesto</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#laboratories" onclick="goToSection('laboratories'); toggleMobileNav(false); return false;" data-i18n="nav_laboratories">Laboratories</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#library" onclick="goToSection('library'); toggleMobileNav(false); return false;" data-i18n="nav_library">Library</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#tools" onclick="goToSection('tools'); toggleMobileNav(false); return false;" data-i18n="nav_tools">Tools</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#join" onclick="goToSection('join'); toggleMobileNav(false); return false;" data-i18n="nav_join">Join</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="success-wrap">
    <div id="success-message" class="success-message">
      <strong data-i18n="join_success">You’re in. Collectividual is still taking form — you’ll hear from it soon.</strong>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main>
    <div id="home-page" class="page active">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="orb one"></div>
        <div class="orb two"></div>
        <div class="orb three"></div>
        <div class="container hero-grid">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow" data-i18n="hero_eyebrow">psycho-social · cultural · creative</div>
            <h1 data-i18n="hero_title">For the life that refuses to remain private.</h1>
            <p class="hero-copy sans" data-i18n="hero_copy">Collectividual is a psycho-social and cultural project for reflection, experimentation, shared language, and symbolic tools. It begins from a simple belief: resilience, meaning, imagination, and livability are not produced alone. They are made in relation, in tension, in memory, and in shared life.</p>
            <div class="cta-row">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#join" onclick="goToSection('join'); return false;" data-i18n="hero_cta_primary">Enter the archive</a>
              <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#laboratories" onclick="goToSection('laboratories'); return false;" data-i18n="hero_cta_secondary">Begin with the labs</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="small-label" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px">
              <span style="display:inline-block;height:14px;width:14px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid rgba(233,127,51,.2);background:radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(233,127,51,0.9) 0%, rgba(233,127,51,0.55) 38%, rgba(125,156,151,0.18) 72%, rgba(235,235,227,0.9) 100%);box-shadow:0 0 14px rgba(233,127,51,.18)"></span>
              <span data-i18n="hero_card_label">Manifesto fragment</span>
            </div>
            <div class="manifesto-fragment" data-i18n="hero_card_quote">We are not only individuals. We are not only collectives. We are collectividuals.</div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <p class="card-copy" data-i18n="hero_card_copy">A project about relational resilience, symbolic life, shared language, and formats that help thought move between people.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="manifesto" class="section">
        <div class="container section-grid">
          <div>
            <div class="small-label" data-i18n="manifesto_label">Manifesto</div>
            <h2 data-i18n="manifesto_title">Against isolated survival. Toward shared language.</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="body-copy">
            <p data-i18n="manifesto_p1">Collectividual begins from a simple proposition: much of what we are taught to endure alone is not a private failure. It is a relational wound, a historical condition, a collective difficulty without enough public language.</p>
            <p data-i18n="manifesto_p2">This project turns psychological insight into public language, symbolic tools, experimental forms, and cultural practices people can return to, carry, and share.</p>
            <p data-i18n="manifesto_p3">Not a wellness brand. Not a therapy clinic. Not a corporate language of resilience. A place to think, make, and test forms that resist the pressure to become only an individual.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="laboratories" class="section muted-section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-top">
